  <brief_title>Robotic-assisted Gait Training Combined With Transcranial Direct Current Stimulation to Maximize Gait Recovery After Stroke</brief_title>
  <official_title>Robotic-assisted Gait Training Combined With Transcranial Direct Current Stimulation to Maximize Gait Recovery After Stroke: A Double-blind, Randomized, Controlled Trial</official_title>
