    <description>tDCS will be applied on the primary motor cortex of the lower limb in the impared hemisphere before robotic-assisted gait training. Anodal tDCS will be applied with an intensity of 2mA for 20 min. Sham tDCS will be applied with an intensity of 2mA just for 1 min, after which the current will be slowly tapered down to 0 over a several seconds.</description>
